data.description: It's not often that a home with all these new upgrades and at this price-point becomes available, especially given the low inventory. This beautifully redone home boasts a brand new kitchen complete with stainless steel appliances and a cozy breakfast nook. The living room is a great size, filled with lots of bright natural light. The bedrooms are spacious and come with large walk-in closets. The basement is unfinished, but it provides a great opportunity to add more square footage to the home.
